When: Sat Nov 14 09 10:00 PM
Where: Cafe Nine, 250 State Street, New Haven, CT, 6511, US


The Elm City will burn to the sounds of Beehive Rock as the Queen & The Montez Boys torch their favorite original music hang. The Nine is the swingin'-est place to hear new tunes, 7 nights a week, and now there's FREE PARKING BEHIND THE CLUB!!! We're shoutin' about it, and if you've ever tried to park in New Haven, you will be, too!!! Log on to www.cafenine.com for all the news, and make the scene with all the other hip cats and kittens!
